Operation.useCase:
Use case 1:
An Active workspace user selects a node in the Architecture Modeler tab and expands to show only the complying tracelinks. This operation will return only the complying tracelinks information from the saved diagram data and also update the diagram data to persist the complying tracelinks expansion action. This is done in order to restore the diagram to the same level of expansion when the user opens the diagram from the saved digram data.

Use case 2:
An Active workspace user selects a product and clicks on the Architecture Modeler tab. System responds by returning all the elements and relations from the saved diagram created for the product.

Operation.useCase:
Use case 1:
In Active workspace, user selects a product and clicks on the Map tab. On click of Awb0Element object from structure system responds by adding the new elements and connectivity relations to the matrix. User then selects Awb0Element object from Content list by clicking on tile icon, as a result the element gets added to the matrix and its connectivity with the existing column elements will be represented.

Use case 2:
In Active workspace user selects a cell in the Map tab and selects command to create a connection. This operation will return newly created connection object starting from the selected row Awb0Element object and ending on the selected column Awb0Element object.

Operation.useCase:
An Active Workspace user selects an object in the Architecture Modeler tab and clicks on the expansion link to expand its relations. System responds by building new shapes for the related objects and relations. User clicks to open the legends section where he/she sees the localized names of the objects and relations. User then selects the types of objects and relations from the legends section to be filtered out. System responds by removing the corresponding shapes from the tab.

A string which specifies the user action. Valid values  are as following -
OpenDiagram - This action opens the saved diagram when the user clicks on the  Architecture tab.

Expand.InConnections - This action returns  the incoming connections of the given Awb0Element object(s).
Expand.OutConnections - This action  returns the outgoing connection of the given Awb0Element object(s).
AddToDiagram - This action adds  the given Awb0Element  object(s) to the diagram.
RemoveFromDiagram - This action removes the given  Awb0Element object(s) from the diagram.
InsertLevel - This actions inserts a newly created Awb0Element  object above the given Awb0Element object(s).

CreateConnection - This action  creates a PSConnection object(or the given subtype) between the given Awb0Element objects.

DeleteElement - This action  deletes the given Awb0Element  object from the system.
